Observation:
Use the textbox to enter "Keneth" and press "Search", then find and click the 1st search result.
    Action:

```
agent.click_xpath("//*[@id='search-text']")
agent.type("Keneth")
agent.click_xpath("//*[@id='search']")
# Calculate the page of the 1st result. Each page contains three results
page = (1 - 1) // 3
agent.click_xpath(f"//*[@id='pagination']/li[{page + 3}]/a")
# Calculate the location of the 1st result. Each page contains three results
remainder = 1 % 3
location = 3 if remainder == 0 else remainder
agent.click_xpath(f"//*[@id='page-content']/div[{location}]/a")
```
